## What we supply

- Cold- and hot-box binder systems for moulding and core-making
- Release coatings for ferrous and non-ferrous alloys, including dip and spray products
- Auxiliary materials: additives, modifiers, tooling cleaners, and lubricants

## How we work

1. Audit the current process and review casting samples.
2. Select materials, define application parameters, and prepare documentation.
3. Train operators and stay on-site until stable quality metrics are achieved.